Tracks on this CD:

1-5. Ravel - Piano Concerto in G, I
6-12. Bartok - Music for Strings, Percussion, and Celesta, II
13-16. Copland -Appalachian Spring (Sections 1, 2, 5, and 6)
17. Webern - Five Orchestral Pieces, IV

22. Varèse - Poeme electronique (excerpt)
23-24. Reich - Music for 18 Musicians (excerpt)
25-27. Saariaho - From the Grammar of Dreams (Songs 1, 3, and 4)
28. Thomas - "If You Ever Been Down" Blues
29. Ellington - "Conga Brava"
30. Parker - "Out of Nowhere"
31. Davis - Bitches Brew (excerpt)
32. Gershwin - Prelude No. 1
33. Bernstein - West Side Story, Dance at Gym: Meeting Scene
34. "Cool"
35. Yoruba drumming - "Ako"
36. South African popular song - "Anoku Gonda"
